nd children to stay with me in a normal home environment, while I received premium therapy at the hospital daily. It changed everything.&ldquo;",[76304,76517],"\"Living in a service villa during my stroke rehabilitation allowed my wife and children to stay with me in a normal home environment, while I received premium therapy at the hospital daily. It changed everything.&#34;",[76304,76517],"\"Living in a service villa during my stroke rehabilitation allowed my wife and children to stay with me in a normal home environment, while I received premium therapy at the hospital daily. It changed everything.&rdquo;",[77397,77598],"&quot;As a caregiver, having doctor visits right at our homestay stay gave me immense peace of mind. I could manage my work remotely while knowing professional medical supervision was available once a day.\"",[77397,77598],"&ldquo;As a caregiver, having doctor visits right at our homestay stay gave me immense peace of mind. I could manage my work remotely while knowing professional medical supervision was available once a day.\"",[77397,77598],"&#34;As a caregiver, having doctor visits right at our homestay stay gave me immense peace of mind. I could manage my work remotely while knowing professional medical supervision was available once a day.\"",[77397,77598],"&rdquo;As a caregiver, having doctor visits right at our homestay stay gave me immense peace of mind. I could manage my work remotely while knowing professional medical supervision was available once a day.\"",[77397,77598],"\"As a caregiver, having doctor visits right at our homestay stay gave me immense peace of mind. I could manage my work remotely while knowing professional medical supervision was available once a day.&quot;",[77397,77598],"\"As a caregiver, having doctor visits right at our homestay stay gave me immense peace of mind. I could manage my work remotely while knowing professional medical supervision was available once a day.&ldquo;",[77397,77598],"\"As a caregiver, having doctor visits right at our homestay stay gave me immense peace of mind. I could manage my work remotely while knowing professional medical supervision was available once a day.&#34;",[77397,77598],"\"As a caregiver, having doctor visits right at our homestay stay gave me immense peace of mind. I could manage my work remotely while knowing professional medical supervision was available once a day.&rdquo;",[77787,77824],"Caregiver for Parkinson&apos;s Patient, UK",[77787,77824],"Caregiver for Parkinson&lsquo;s Patient, UK",[77787,77824],"Caregiver for Parkinson&#39;s Patient, UK",[77787,77824],"Caregiver for Parkinson&rsquo;s Patient, UK",[78489,78689],"&quot;Registering our cottage as an accommodation partner was simple and has brought steady rental support to our family, while giving us the privilege of helping patient families feel at home in Edappal.\"",[78489,78689],"&ldquo;Registering our cottage as an accommodation partner was simple and has brought steady rental support to our family, while giving us the privilege of helping patient families feel at home in Edappal.\"",[78489,78689],"&#34;Registering our cottage as an accommodation partner was simple and has brought steady rental support to our family, while giving us the privilege of helping patient families feel at home in Edappal.\"",[78489,78689],"&rdquo;Registering our cottage as an accommodation partner was simple and has brought steady rental support to our family, while giving us the privilege of helping patient families feel at home in Edappal.\"",[78489,78689],"\"Registering our cottage as an accommodation partner was simple and has brought steady rental support to our family, while giving us the privilege of helping patient families feel at home in Edappal.&quot;",[78489,78689],"\"Registering our cottage as an accommodation partner was simple and has brought steady rental support to our family, while giving us the privilege of helping patient families feel at home in Edappal.&ldquo;",[78489,78689],"\"Registering our cottage as an accommodation partner was simple and has brought steady rental support to our family, while giving us the privilege of helping patient families feel at home in Edappal.&#34;",[78489,78689],"\"Registering our cottage as an accommodation partner was simple and has brought steady rental support to our family, while giving us the privilege of helping patient families feel at home in Edappal.&rdquo;",[80983,81271],"Based on the patient&apos;s needs and preferences during clinical intake, our team suggests the most suitable stay within a 5 km radius of Edappal. Options include private Service Villas (ideal for families), heritage Homestays (for local connection), and modern elevator-connected Apartments.",[80983,81271],"Based on the patient&lsquo;s needs and preferences during clinical intake, our team suggests the most suitable stay within a 5 km radius of Edappal. Options include private Service Villas (ideal for families), heritage Homestays (for local connection), and modern elevator-connected Apartments.",[80983,81271],"Based on the patient&#39;s needs and preferences during clinical intake, our team suggests the most suitable stay within a 5 km radius of Edappal. Options include private Service Villas (ideal for families), heritage Homestays (for local connection), and modern elevator-connected Apartments.",[80983,81271],"Based on the patient&rsquo;s needs and preferences during clinical intake, our team suggests the most suitable stay within a 5 km radius of Edappal. Options include private Service Villas (ideal for families), heritage Homestays (for local connection), and modern elevator-connected Apartments.",[82355,82630],"All clinical therapies, physical rehabilitation, speech therapy, robotic training, and clinical examinations are conducted exclusively at Ayurgreen Hospital&apos;s advanced facilities. Shuttle links are organized to transfer patients safely from their villa to the hospital daily.",[82355,82630],"All clinical 